<div class="cluster center_via_margin margin_bottom flex_around">
    <div class="cluster_block speech_maxwidth flex_around_margin_right">
        <h2>What is it for?</h2>
        <p class="margin_bottom_m">Insulin Buddy is a website for helping you manage your diabetes. It provides a friendly, motivating
            environment in which to record your daily insulin doses taken, blood glucose, weight, and exercise
            measurements. This information is directly linked to your clinician, allowing them to monitor your
            health status and send you encouraging messages.</p>

        <h2>About the creators</h2>
        <p class="margin_bottom">We're a team of university students studying web development at the University of Melbourne. We love
            creating websites, and we love helping other people, so we were excited to do both with Insulin
            Buddy.</p>

        <p class="margin_bottom">You must be logged in to access all of Insulin Buddy's features - contact your clinician to join.</p>    
    </div>

